  <entry>
    <title>Blogging in Hexo</title>
    <link href="/2022/06/14/Blogging-in-Hexo/"/>
    <url>/2022/06/14/Blogging-in-Hexo/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Change-Theme-from-GitHub"><a href="#Change-Theme-from-GitHub" class="headerlink" title="Change Theme (from GitHub)"></a>Change Theme (from GitHub)</h2><ul><li><a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">Fluid</a>  </li><li><a href="https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly">Butterfly</a></li></ul><h3 id="Step-1-CLone"><a href="#Step-1-CLone" class="headerlink" title="Step 1: CLone"></a>Step 1: CLone</h3><p>Code:  </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> [网络路径] [本地路径]</span><br><span class="line">```  </span><br><span class="line">Example: Set [Butterfly](https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly) as the theme  </span><br><span class="line">``` bash</span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly.git themes/butterfly</span><br><span class="line">```  </span><br><span class="line">Notes:  </span><br><span class="line">- <span class="string">&quot;git clone&quot;</span> 是克隆指令；  </span><br><span class="line">- [网络路径] 通常有.git结尾。不是网址，而是由Code处复制而来的URL；  </span><br><span class="line">![img](D:\Learning\iblog\<span class="built_in">source</span>\img\Blogging-in-Hexo-1.png)  </span><br><span class="line">- themes/butterfly不是[本地路径]的唯一选择，只是存入themes文件夹更容易查找，因为搭建网页时Hexo已经在本地自动生成了这个名字的文件夹。同理，创建/butterfly文件夹是为了便于分类多个主题；  </span><br><span class="line">- [网络路径]和[本地路径]之间有一个空格。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">### Step 2: Configurate  </span></span><br><span class="line">- 在本地内容中找到Hexo生成的_config.yml文件。这个文件包含了一系列设置参数；  </span><br><span class="line">- 打开该文件（请勿使用Window自带的记事本，VSCode可以打开并编辑该类文件）；  </span><br><span class="line">- 找到theme一栏，将冒号后面的内容改成主题的名字并保存。如下是butterfly的例子；  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>theme: buttefly</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- 更新部署到远端，再刷新个人博客就能实现（可能需要等待一段时间）。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>hexo g<br>hexo d<br>&#96;&#96;&#96;</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
